  "text": "Sarkar [CITATION_1] has also noted an almost triangular shape of the seiche amplitude longitudinal profile. However, Sarkar finds the maximum amplitude to be at one fifth of the total length of the cylinder array, which is different to our finding that the maximum amplitude is at mid-length. This difference could be attributed to non-uniformity of the flow within the cylinder array in Sarkar's experiments.",
